```{r pancreas 32323087, include=FALSE}

PMID_32323087 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32323087', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32323087 <- paste0(PMID_32323087$journal,' ', PMID_32323087$year, ' ', PMID_32323087$month,';', PMID_32323087$volume,'(', PMID_32323087$number,'):', PMID_32323087$pages)

PubMed_32323087 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32323087$eprint)

doi_32323087 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32323087$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
